Tab B—My suggested Talking Points at the NSC meeting inviting discussion of the agenda issues;
                                copies of two IG charts;Attached but not printed, at Tab B, are
                                    suggested talking points and copies of two IG charts.

Tab E—GAC Chairman William Graham’s letter to you proposing a
                                specific START package related to
                                the Scowcroft Commission;

Retain the limit of 5,000 ballistic missile warheads and the
                                    2,500 sublimit on ICBM
                                    warheads;

Limit both sides to 1.9 million kilograms of ballistic missile
                                    throwweight and a .5 million kilogram sublimit on MIRVed
                                    ICBM throwweight;
